      Fix crash when <varname>log_min_error_statement</varname> logging runs out
      of memory (Tom)
     </para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
     <para>
      Fix incorrect handling of some foreign-key corner cases (Tom)
     </para>
    </listitem>

